703
00:48:55,749 --> 00:48:57,049
Astaga.

704
00:48:58,979 --> 00:49:03,019
Senyumannya seperti debu mikro.

705
00:49:03,019 --> 00:49:05,489
Sangat mematikan.

706
00:49:09,390 --> 00:49:12,630
